    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An AI menace is invading your motherboard! Can you survive?</strong>!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404890/extras/35dc47b7ea6cf35da01639abfd098d83.webp?t=1740837020\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404890/extras/35dc47b7ea6cf35da01639abfd098d83.poster.avif?t=1740837020\" class=\"bb_img\" width=128 height=128 /></picture></span><br><strong>Neon D-Fence Remastered</strong> is a fast-paced, beginner-friendly tower defense game with an arcade twist! Easy to pick up, fun to master—build your defenses, survive waves of enemies, and aim for the highest score!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404890/extras/9a93a0c6ff1df539179c787bea871fa1.webp?t=1740837020\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404890/extras/9a93a0c6ff1df539179c787bea871fa1.poster.avif?t=1740837020\" class=\"bb_img\" width=128 height=128 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404890/extras/c5e71e9003679fb8860cd4b7d14775ef.webp?t=1740837020\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404890/extras/c5e71e9003679fb8860cd4b7d14775ef.poster.avif?t=1740837020\" class=\"bb_img\" width=128 height=128 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404890/extras/6fa58a7803705cda875fcd63f5d66d96.poster.avif?t=1740837020\" width=128 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404890/extras/6fa58a7803705cda875fcd63f5d66d96.webm?t=1740837020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Defend, Upgrade, and Survive!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple &amp; Fun:</strong> Jump in and start defending right away—no complex rules, just pure action!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>10 Unique Maps:</strong> Test your strategy on a variety of layouts!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build &amp; Upgrade:</strong> Earn &quot;RAM&quot; and &quot;Data&quot; to place powerful towers and unlock awesome upgrades!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Face Waves of Enemies:</strong> From grunts to explosive threats and massive bosses, can you outlast them all?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404890/extras/b5239c45f461840390a59d8760459639.poster.avif?t=1740837020\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404890/extras/b5239c45f461840390a59d8760459639.webm?t=1740837020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Designed for Everyone</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're new to tower defense games or a longtime fan looking for a fresh challenge, <strong>Neon D-Fence Remastered</strong> is designed to be <strong>accessible, exciting, and endlessly replayable</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So, are you ready to defend your motherboard and claim the <strong>ultimate high score</strong>?</p>",
